Usage: setSelectedPtnCut [-help] <X1> <Y1> <X2> <Y2> <PartitionName>

-help               # Prints out the command usage
<X1>                # coordinate x1 of the partition cut area (float, required)
<Y1>                # coordinate y1 of the partition cut area (float, required)
<X2>                # coordinate x2 of the partition cut area (float, required)
<Y2>                # coordinate y2 of the partition cut area (float, required)
<PartitionName>     # name of the partition cut area (string, required)